n at Kristen's request I have declined them all awaiting an invitation from those who are in her guild. I have not found any type of guild structure in AC and was wondering what sort of prerequisite there is for joining your guild. I have seen how in depth Kristen has gotten into EQ and those she calls family and as I have been hunting mainly alone the last 8 lvls in AC I believe the FTFL to be just the thing to add some flavor to my quest for RP. ::Kristen is poking me again She says &quot;HI!&quot;::<br>
